<section class="component  ">

  
  <div class="component-text-block">
  
    <div class="component-description">
                    <h2 id="the-tutorium-in-intensive-english-cea-accreditation" class="__title visible">The Tutorium in Intensive English CEA Accreditation</h2>
                    </div>

    <figure class="_image captioned-image image-left-third">
  <img src="https://tie.uic.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/403/2019/08/cea-accredited-400px-2019.jpg" alt="CEA logo that states "Accredited by CEA"">
  </figure>
  
  <p>The Tutorium in Intensive English is accredited by the Commission on English Language Program Accreditation (<a href="https://cea-accredit.org/">CEA</a>) for the period April 2017 through April 2027 and agrees to uphold the CEA Standards for English Language Programs and Institutions. CEA is recognized by the U.S. Secretary of Education as a nationally recognized accrediting agency for English language programs and institutions in the U.S. For further information about this accreditation, please contact CEA, (703) 665-3400, <a href="https://cea-accredit.org/">cea-accredit.org</a>.</p>



  
</div>

  
</section>

    

    
      

